hands_on_practices.solution:
我们令单原子弹性碰撞速率等于单原子三体损失速率，
$$\Gamma_{\rm el}=n\,K_{\rm el},\qquad 
\Gamma_{3}=n^2\,L_3,\qquad
n_c:\;\; \Gamma_{\rm el}=\Gamma_{3}\;\Rightarrow\;n_c=\frac{K_{\rm el}}{L_3}\,. $$

1.  幺正极限弹性速率系数：
$$\sigma_{\rm el}(v)=\frac{4\pi}{k^2}
=\frac{4\pi\hbar^2}{\mu^2v^2},\qquad \mu=\frac m2.$$
因此
$$K_{\rm el}
=\langle\sigma_{\rm el}v\rangle
=\int_0^\infty\frac{4\pi\hbar^2}{\mu^2v^2}\;v\;
4\pi v^2\Bigl(\frac{\mu}{2\pi k_BT}\Bigr)^{3/2}
e^{-\mu v^2/(2k_BT)}\,dv.$$
提出常数并进行计算
$$\int_0^\infty v\,e^{-\alpha v^2}dv=\frac1{2\alpha},\quad \alpha=\frac\mu{2k_BT},$$
可得
$$K_{\rm el}
=\frac{4\pi\hbar^2}{\mu^2}\,4\pi\Bigl(\frac{\mu}{2\pi k_BT}\Bigr)^{3/2}
\frac{k_BT}{\mu}
=\frac{16\pi^2\hbar^2}{\mu^3}\frac{\mu^{3/2}}{(2\pi k_B T)^{3/2}}k_B T
=\frac{16\pi^2 \hbar^2}{\mu^{3/2}(2\pi)^{3/2}(k_B T)^{1/2}}
=\frac{4\sqrt{2\pi}\hbar^2}{\mu^{3/2}(k_BT)^{1/2}}
=\frac{4\sqrt{2\pi}\hbar^2}{(m/2)^{3/2}(k_BT)^{1/2}}
=\frac{32\sqrt{\pi}\hbar^2}{m^{3/2}(k_BT)^{1/2}}\,. $$

2.  三体复合速率系数：
$$L_3=C_3\,\frac{\hbar^3a^2}{m^2k_BT}\,. $$

3.  临界密度：
$$n_c=\frac{K_{\rm el}}{L_3}
=\frac{\displaystyle\frac{32\sqrt{\pi}\hbar^2}{m^{3/2}(k_BT)^{1/2}}}
{\displaystyle C_3\,\frac{\hbar^3a^2}{m^2k_BT}}
=\frac{32\sqrt{\pi}}{C_3} \frac{\hbar^2 m^2 k_B T}{\hbar^3 a^2 m^{3/2} (k_B T)^{1/2}}
=\frac{32\sqrt{\pi m k_B T}}{C_3 \hbar a^2}\,. $$

我们从速率方程开始
$$\frac{dn}{dt}=-L_3(B(t))\,n^3\,. $$  
分离变量：
$$\frac{dn}{n^3}=-L_3(B(t))\,dt\,. $$  
从 $t=0$ ($n=n_i$) 积分到 $t=T$ ($n=n_f$)，其中 $T=(B_f-B_i)/\alpha=\delta B/\alpha$：
$$\int_{n_i}^{n_f}\!n^{-3}dn=-\int_{0}^{T}\!L_{3,peak}\Bigl[1+\bigl(\tfrac{B(t)-B_{res}}{\delta B/2}\bigr)^2\Bigr]^{-1}dt\,. $$  
计算左侧：
$$\int n^{-3}dn=\Bigl[-\frac{1}{2n^2}\Bigr]_{n_i}^{n_f}=\frac{1}{2n_i^2}-\frac{1}{2n_f^2}\,. $$  
对于右侧，令
$$x=\frac{B(t)-B_{res}}{\delta B/2}=-1+\frac{2t}{T},\quad dt=\frac{T}{2}dx,\quad x: -1\to1,$$  
所以
$$\int_{0}^{T}\frac{dt}{1+x^2}
=\frac{T}{2}\int_{-1}^{1}\frac{dx}{1+x^2}
=\frac{T}{2}\Bigl[\arctan x\Bigr]_{-1}^{1}
=\frac{T\pi}{4}\,. $$  
因此
$$\frac{1}{2n_i^2}-\frac{1}{2n_f^2}
=-L_{3,peak}\frac{T\pi}{4}
=-\,\frac{L_{3,peak}\,\pi\,\delta B}{4\alpha}\,. $$  
乘以2并求解 $n_f$：
$$\frac{1}{n_i^2}-\frac{1}{n_f^2}
=-\frac{L_{3,peak}\,\pi\,\delta B}{2\alpha}
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
\frac{1}{n_f^2}
=\frac{1}{n_i^2}+\frac{\pi\,n_i^2\,L_{3,peak}\,\delta B}{2\alpha}\,\frac{1}{n_i^2}
=\frac{1}{n_i^2}\Bigl(1+\frac{\pi\,n_i^2\,L_{3,peak}\,\delta B}{2\alpha}\Bigr)\,. $$  
于是
$$n_f
=\frac{n_i}{\sqrt{1+\dfrac{\pi\,n_i^2\,L_{3,peak}\,\delta B}{2\alpha}}}\,, 
\quad
f_{loss}=1-\frac{n_f}{n_i}
=1-\frac{1}{\sqrt{1+\frac{\pi\,n_i^2\,L_{3,peak}\,\delta B}{2\alpha}}}\,. $$
